msg: Rename the ControlTestUtil class to ControlContainerContextManager.  This class is a manager for the CCC in that it delegates several lifecycle and utility calls through so that the test author doesn't need to worry so much about managing it.
Also is a place to allow a new CCC implementation to be swapped in easily -- plug point for that coming later.
